{"tid":1607544,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"經濟戰八月成績表。","createTime":"2019-10-01T01:33:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T13:32:36.000Z","uid":306689,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cd0d645e0a6004b8689c42ba230e7ac3b6b3ad25","tid":1607544,"uid":306689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T01:33:05.000Z","msg":"早點成立黃絲美元經濟圈吧！<br />\n<br />\n如下所述：<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;》【全民撳錢】金管局：8月港元存款減少1110億元 (18:17)<br />\n<br />\n文章日期：2019年9月30日<br />\n<br />\n8月份有人發起「全民撳錢」活動，據金管局最新公布的數字，8月份本港銀行的港元存款按月減少1110.79億元，跌幅達到1.6%，由6.95萬億減至6.84萬億元。當中以活期存款減幅最大，跌4.7%，儲蓄存款跌2.6%。無獨有偶，美元存款相應上升，折合港元的升幅達1325.22億元，或升2.7%。整體而言，所有存款上升0.2%至13.63萬億元。......<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1569837207161&amp;issue=20190930\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1569837207161%26issue%3D20190930&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdYE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=c7f602e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1569837207161%26issue%3D20190930&h=429e5fa0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1569837207161&amp;issue=20190930</a>"},{"pid":"256d5dc489344a2dfe35a5f171635c49f67c7493","tid":1607544,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T01:41:49.000Z","msg":"咁勁?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a14ed481499176e45dc5711039d31933fc9d048","tid":1607544,"uid":95409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T01:48:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dea20752e936761cf86d172f202ab6ca385f6560","tid":1607544,"uid":60977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T01:49:32.000Z","msg":"長期戰線黎"},{"pid":"dfbc1f121878de7477df87b6b88ca59f7cd170ce","tid":1607544,"uid":1747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,